data.description: Beautiful, unique lakefront home awaits you in Carolina Equestrian Village! Step out onto the large deck to experience the plentiful views of the lake or wander down to the backyard firepit to enjoy a relaxing evening! The main floor provides an open concept living area to include the primary bedroom suite and laundry. Downstairs you will find 2 additional bedrooms and full bath as well as a living area, an additional fireplace as well as access to the fenced in yard. Above the detached garage there is a spacious game room for you to enjoy! Carolina Equestrian Village is a gated community boasting 2 lakes, community pool and horse facilities for rent.
